channel.title: RS-Reborn Development Team
channel.description:
[center][img]http://img850.imageshack.us/img850/4839/rsrlogo2.png[/img][/center] [hr] [b][u]What am I looking for:[/u][/b] I am looking for another two server programmers to work on the base, one to two programmers to make the website and a few content programmers. I also could use people to get information if you would like to apply for this send me a pm and we can talk :) [b][u]The base:[/u][/b] The base is design by me from the ground up. The base currently has the following done: [ul][li]Cache loading[/li] [li]Object definitions loading via cache[/li] [li]Maps loading via cache[/li] [li]Clipping loading (Walking and projectile)[/li] [li]Pathfinding[/li] [li]Content system[/li] [li]Combat system[/li] [li]Action system[/li][/ul] and much more. [b][u]Application:[/u][/b] Note: If you apply you must have a good understand of java or php.
How old are you?: Skype name: Position: How long have you coded?: Can you show me some previous work?: What time zone are you in?: How long will you be on everyday?: Why do you want to become part of this server?:
[b][u]The current team:[/u][/b] [ul][li]X-Logic - Paul [Server Programmer / Leader][/li] [li]Wizard Jesse - Jesse [Content Programmer][/li][/ul] Thanks, X-logic.
